('94383','32504','5','Bungalow with panoramic views and pool in Puntiro'),
('94384','32505','5','Puntiro is just 15 minutes from Palma and the airport away. In 5 Min you reach the next golf course. This quiet residential area is popular with villa owners who are looking for the short connection to Palma and for a home on a quiet larger plot. The house in the bungalow style was created in 2003 and is in very good condition. Living room, kitchen, 5 bedrooms 4 bathrooms (1BR with separate entrance and bathroom en suite) are on one level. Features include, oil central heating, air conditioning, fireplace, fitted kitchen, fitted bathroom and wood - double glazed windows with aluminum shutters. The house is sold unfurnished. The garden and outdoor area has a beautiful mediterranean vegetation. A 5x10m large pool and a covered barbecue area are the perfect place to relax'),
